offer_summary.job_description: Joining the team is a unique opportunity to work with modern financial systems, focusing on scalability and maintaining high availability and resilience. The company has open positions in multiple domains across the organization.
requirements: Experience with React.js (front-end) or Node.js (back-end), Redux (state management), Context API, Hook.
CI/CD Experience. Familiarity with Webpack and Babel.
Experience with NoSQL databases (MongoDB, Firebase), SQL in backend systems using Node.js.
Familiarity with serverless architecture (e.g., AWS). Experience with AWS services and cloud infrastructure in projects.
benefits: Challenging international projects in a Scandinavian business culture.
Transparently built relations based on trust and fair play.
Co-financed benefits: Medicover card, Multisport card.
